ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A dinner-party and book-club that I get to attend every week with my brilliant new friends. A whirlwind tour of the most interesting new humanities research going on at Yale.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I have no idea yet. So far it's granted me incredible perspective, both in terms of thinking about the place of my work in the academic ecosystem, and the ways in which graduate pedagogy and cross-disciplinary discussion can and should take place.
